AUDIO: 'Hi, I\'m Alex Bosco, one of the creators at Luma. When creating the launch video for Luma agents, we wanted to use Luma to create case studies for three different creative industries and how they would benefit from the Luma [music] workflow. First, we upload our script.'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Starting with character development, we create a bunch of different characters to choose from. [music] We find three that we like and build from there. We have to see what they look like from all angles to ensure consistency [music]'

[00:24] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
